{
  "stem": "24231.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rahm was the camp commandant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and he once in a while, you know, brought sometimes the horse to the-- to the blacksmith's also.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- he sort of knew my father, that he was able to to fix the horses right away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he-- he-- he saved me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day-- one day, all of a sudden, we had a shooting around-- around the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, news spread that the Russians are in the area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I used to have another guy who would be helping me out cleaning the horses in the morning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, he said-- this guy was a real adventurist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He lost his parents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't have anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was-- he was the only one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was an orphan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said, I'm going to go out, out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he went out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he found that there were Russian tanks around-- around the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And somehow the Russians adopted him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everyday, all of a sudden he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He went with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the evening, he-- he came back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and they were giving him food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so-- and then things spread out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, we are free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The only thing is there was, at that time, there was some-- there was typhoid.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And people-- people didn't-- they didn't want people to-- to get out of the ghetto right away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I had a pair of horses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I-- my father said, well, we are not going to wait for anybody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We just load up-- load up whatever we-- we have, mother, my-- my sister.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I had two friends, one of them, [INAUDIBLE], he is in Boston here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Another one is in Israel, this fellow, [INAUDIBLE], we went.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
